    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per V&V 40 Table 3 at MRL 2. Validation MARE of 8.3% is well within the 15% acceptance criterion. The assurance level is rated High based on the breadth of the validation campaign, the direct relevance of validation conditions to the COU, and the conservative acceptance criteria applied throughout. The model is accepted as sufficiently credible to support the intended regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
